From: Garrett Brown <themagnificentmrb@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 13 Jun 2024 20:04:06 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Fix locating drm headers on Linux

Fixes error:

  vf_deinterlace_v4l2m2m.c:24:10: fatal error: drm_fourcc.h: No such file or directory
     24 | #include <drm_fourcc.h>
        |          ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~

---
 configure | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index ec0a1f4a8b..74d3a34e32 100755
--- a/configure
+++ b/configure
@@ -5770,6 +5770,7 @@ case $target_os in
     linux)
         enable section_data_rel_ro
         enabled_any arm aarch64 && enable_weak linux_perf
+        add_cflags -I/usr/include/drm
         ;;
     irix*)
         target_os=irix
